revisions.description: The initial release of this management information module.

usdSscClientAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdSscClientAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Service Selection Center (SSC) Client component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdSscClientAgentV1.name: usdSscClientAgentV1
usdSscClientAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the SSC Client component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SSC Client component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 2.0 thru 3.0 system releases.
usdSscClientAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the SSC Client application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when DHCP-LS, Web and SSC support objects were added to the MIB.

usdSscClientAgentV2.name: usdSscClientAgentV2
usdSscClientAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the SSC Client component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SSC Client component is supported in
        the Unisphere RX 3.1 thru 3.x system releases.
usdSscClientAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the SSC Client application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the version number object was added to the MIB.

usdSscClientAgentV3.name: usdSscClientAgentV3
usdSscClientAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the SSC Client component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the SSC Client component is supported in
        the Unisphere RX 4.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdSscClientAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the SSC Client application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
